Twitter Streaming API

  • Application Programming Interface:

  • https://apps.twitter.com/app/new, need cellphone number

  • interact with webservice
  • for developers to interact with the webservices and to access data in a programmatic way.

R packages

library(twitteR) # OAuth access to twitter API

library(tm) # textming, breaks down and clean chunks of text

library(wordcloud) 

library(RColorBrewer) # create fun colors!

library(ggplot2) # better plotting functions

library(qdap) # Sentiment Analysis

library(stringr) # make it easier to deal with strings

twitteR is the package that helps set up twitter

Obtain Data

  • Authorization
setup_twitter_oauth(API.key, 
                    API.secret, 
                    Access.token, 
                    Access.secret)
  • Search Twitter by keywords / hashtags
  • Download tweets from an account by user ID.

Sentiment Analysis

Sentiment Analysis

  • assign a sentiment score (-1 to 1) to each sentence utilizing the sentiment dictionary

  • Default sentiment dictionary: Hu, M., & Liu, B. (2004). Mining opinion features in customer reviews. National Conference on Artificial Intelligence.

  • Two-sample t-test on mean difference of sentimental scores:

      Hillary Clinton V.S. Bernie Sanders
  sample mean estimates:
  0.002245229 0.017733092 
  p-value = 2.415e-05
  95 percent confidence interval:
   -0.022671009 -0.008304717

Discussion

  • more polarized sentiment towards Hillary Clinton than Bernie Sanders
  • time points: April 12th v.s. April 30th.
